verbose_text: In the present study, it was demonstrated that H 2 O 2 treatment significantly induced oxidative stress damage and apoptosis in primary hippocampal neurons, and the NOX2-NLRP1 inflammasome pathway was important in H 2 O 2 -induced neuronal senescence and damage.
